rows.label: qst200317_msg0001
rows.name: Oh, hey! It's you guys!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0002
rows.name:
We saved them.
They're safe!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0003
rows.name:
Thank you! You're a good sort!
Despite your appearance...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0004
rows.name:
But the Gogol...got away.
Apologies.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0005
rows.name: The...Gogol?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0006
rows.name:
Ah, the rockfall was caused by
a Gogol, actually. But it kinda
got away from us...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0007
rows.name: What? Are you being serious?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0008
rows.name:
'Cos one of them showed up here
just a moment ago and started going
crazy!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0009
rows.name: What?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0010
rows.name: Are you certain?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0011
rows.name:
Yeah! I know what I saw!
It went after the workers...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0012
rows.name:
It grabbed a girl and climbed to
the top of the tower, making a
terrible racket as it went...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0013
rows.name:
I'm telling you, it was a mess!
Luckily, Luxurian soldiers were here to
chase it off, so damage was minimal...

rows.label: qst200317_msg0014
rows.name:
What the hell? It pretended to
run away, then attacked the town?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0015
rows.name:
Grrah! Unforgivable!
I will hunt the Gogol down!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0016
rows.name: ...One moment, Jikarao.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0017
rows.name:
...Grrm?
What about the hunt?!

rows.label: qst200317_msg0018
rows.name:
Meleph, what's up?
Thought of something?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0019
rows.name:
Mmm...
I can't make sense of it.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0020
rows.name:
The Gogol did not run in the direction
of the town, nor could it have
climbed the pillar.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0021
rows.name:
It may be quick, but could it have really
attacked the town from there?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0023
rows.name: ...Grh?

rows.label: qst200317_msg0024
rows.name:
You make a good point.
...Let's look around a bit.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0025
rows.name:
Jikarao, the hunt can wait. First,
let's talk to the townspeople.

rows.label: qst200317_msg0026
rows.name: ...Hrmgh.
